descriptionHtml:
The results of my efforts to make a beautiful character that seems anatomically grounded in reality.  I am pretty pleased with the results.  I tried to stay away from the super anime look a lot of people seem to go for, as it's not my thing.  I also included my bodyslide preset, if anyone wants the exact look in the screenshots.  This is my first time uploading anything to the nexus, so forgive me if I did something horribly wrong.  CONSTRUCTIVE criticism is welcome, but dont be a douche.  Please Endorse if you enjoy the mod!

[size=3]I am working on making a follower .esp for her, stay tuned![/size]

The following mods are required to get the results you see here:

Caliente's Beautiful Bodies Edition -CBBE- by [b]Ousnius and Caliente[/b] http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?
BodySlide and Outfit Studio by [b]Ousnius and Caliente http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49015/?
SG Female Textures Renewal by [b]Hello Santa http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?
RaceMenu by [b]Expired http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?
The Eyes Of Beauty by [b]Gabriel Mailhot as LogRaam[/b] http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?
Brows by [b]Hvergelmir http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?
